{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396290/extras/FloralDesign.gif?t=1740741113\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Manage a flower shop, design bouquets... with a talking flower on your head?!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Puni the Florist</strong> is a cozy flower shop simulation game where you play as &quot;Puni,&quot; an office worker-turned-florist. Run a flower shop, design bouquets, and deal with a weird talking flower that grows on her head.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Express Your Creativity</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fulfill townsfolk\u2019s requests with your own floral designs using unique combinations of flowers and decorations.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Wholesome Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in a silly, light-hearted, and relatable tale of self-discovery of Puni and the Flower.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Learn Floriography</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete flower collections and uncover the language of flowers through your scrapbook.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Decorate Your Shop</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make your shop your own with cute, customizable decor and personal touches.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Befriend the Townsfolks</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meet a quirky cast of characters, uncover their stories, and form lasting friendships.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396290/extras/Lobby.gif?t=1740741113\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396290/extras/DiscordBanner.png?t=1740741113\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3396290?t=1740741113","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396290/c3dcce7eca2fec19f11df6f22b19c6403aab8219/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=17